ks.framework.communicator
Class Communicator

java.lang.Object
  ks.framework.communicator.Communicator
All Implemented Interfaces:
IOutput, IRegistration, org.compunit.interfaces.IComponent
public class Communicator
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.compunit.interfaces.IComponent, IOutput, IRegistration

Responsible for all communication from the server to its clients.

Communicator will need access to an IUserManager object to be able to identify the set of active uers during a broadcast. Note that we read Commands from the client and write messages to the client.

Author:
George T. Heineman (heineman@cs.wpi.edu)
